The unit will NOT have a cartridge port on it - it is an <strong>emulator</strong>, albeit an incredibly low-level one. Besides, said cartridge port would only be useful for <em>one</em> console, and this unit is going to support <strong>multiple</strong> systems (including but not limited to Atari 2600, Sega Master System, Colecovision).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Mon Dec 13, 2004 3:20 pm</p><hr />
